<lb/>Based on the edition included as Appendix I in:
<lb/>Prabhas Chandra Sen: Mahasthan and Its Environs,
<lb/>Rajshahi, Bengal : Varendra Research Society 1929
<lb/>(Varendra Research Society's Monographs, 2)
